data.description:
Fixer upper and almost 10 acres with plenty of potential to build. House has a large driveway, carport and garage. 
Entry to the house has a ramp for handicap access. Interior has a large family room and large kitchen and dining room combo with easy access to the side deck or back porch. The 2 bedroom 1 bath home has plenty of space and storage.
Red shed and pool are not staying with the property.
